HOW TO USE:

TCP - navigate to each folder in the "TCP_SOCKET" folder and run the executable file starting with the "TCP_Server" then the "TCP_Client"
- The image will be saved in the same file as the server executable and it is hard coded as a jpg

UDP - navigate to each folder in the "UDP_SOCKET" folder and run the executable file starting with the "UDP_Server" then the "UDP_Client"
- The image will be saved in the same file as the server executable and it is hard coded as a jpg